options.content:
Letzter Datenstand: </br>
${stichtagmonat}

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  "time" AS "time",
  post_video_view_time
FROM facebookinsightsownposts
WHERE
  $__timeFilter("time")
ORDER BY 1

SELECT  CONCAT(REPEAT(" ", GREATEST(0,10 - CHAR_LENGTH('Follower / Abonnenten in Mio. | ${Month:text} $Jahr'))), 'Follower / Abonnenten in Mio. | ${Month:text} $Jahr'), 
FROM(
SELECT 'Follower / Abonnenten in Mio. | ${Month:text} $Jahr' as Interaktionen
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.facebook`
LIMIT 1
)

WITH current_value AS(
	SELECT followers AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
past_value AS(
	SELECT followers AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id AND $comp_condition
)
SELECT  ROUND((current_sum/past_sum)-1,2) as ig_difference FROM current_value, past_value

WITH current_value AS(
	SELECT abonnements AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
past_value AS(
	SELECT abonnements AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id AND $comp_condition
)
SELECT  ROUND((current_sum/past_sum)-1,2) as yt_difference FROM current_value, past_value

WITH current_value AS(
	SELECT followers AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
past_value AS(
	SELECT followers AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id AND $comp_condition
)
SELECT  ROUND((current_sum/past_sum)-1,2) as tt_difference FROM current_value, past_value

WITH current_value AS(
	SELECT page_follows AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
past_value AS(
	SELECT page_follows AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id AND $comp_condition
)
SELECT  ROUND((current_sum/past_sum)-1,2) as fb_difference FROM current_value, past_value

WITH fb_current_value AS(
	SELECT page_follows/1000000 AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
fb_past_value AS(
	SELECT page_follows/1000000 AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id AND $comp_condition
),
ig_current_value AS(
	SELECT followers/1000000 AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
ig_past_value AS(
	SELECT followers/1000000 AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id AND $comp_condition
),
yt_current_value AS(
	SELECT abonnements/1000000 AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
yt_past_value AS(
	SELECT abonnements/1000000 AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id AND $comp_condition
),
tt_current_value AS(
	SELECT followers/1000000 AS current_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id AND monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
),
tt_past_value AS(
	SELECT followers/1000000 AS past_sum
	FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
	WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id AND $comp_condition
)
SELECT 

ig_past_value.past_sum as ig_old, 
ig_current_value.current_sum as ig_new,
yt_past_value.past_sum as yt_old, 
yt_current_value.current_sum as yt_new,
tt_past_value.past_sum as tt_old, 
tt_current_value.current_sum as tt_new,
fb_past_value.past_sum as fb_old, 
fb_current_value.current_sum as fb_new,
FROM 
fb_past_value,
fb_current_value,
ig_past_value,
ig_current_value,
yt_past_value,
yt_current_value,
tt_past_value, 
tt_current_value

panels.title: Social Media Plattformen in der Übersicht
Top Postings und Übersichtstabellen aktueller Monat je Plattform

options.content: Instagram | ${Month:text} $Jahr

targets.rawSql:
SELECT pot_reichweite_pro_tag, CASE monat
        WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT(tag," Jan.")
        WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT(tag," Feb.")
        WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT(tag," März")
        WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT(tag," Apr.")
        WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT(tag," Mai")
        WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT(tag," Juni")
        WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT(tag," Juli")
        WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT(tag," Aug.")
        WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT(tag," Sep.")
        WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT(tag," Okt.")
        WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT(tag," Nov.")
        WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT(tag," Dez.")
        END as d_time, DATE(jahr,monat,tag) as time
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics_per_day
WHERE CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 13 THEN TRUE 
ELSE monat = $month_as_number END
AND jahr = $Jahr
AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT 
  time,
  CASE videoViews
  WHEN 0 THEN CAST(NULL AS INT)
  ELSE videoViews END AS videoViews,
  reach,
  type,
  link,
  post as Post,
  Interaktionen 
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_top_posts_nach_interaktionen
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id 
ORDER BY Interaktionen DESC LIMIT 100

SELECT 
  time,
  CASE videoViews
  WHEN 0 THEN CAST(NULL AS INT)
  ELSE videoViews END AS videoViews,
  reach,
  type,
  link,
  post as Post,
  Interaktionen 
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_top_posts_nach_interaktionen
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id 
ORDER BY videoViews DESC LIMIT 100

SELECT
 createTime,
 Thumbnail,
  message,
  link,
  type,
  reach,
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_top_story_elemente_nach_pot_reichweite
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id 
ORDER BY reach DESC limit 100

SELECT
 createTime,
 Thumbnail,
  message,
  link,
  type,
  reach,
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_top_story_elemente_nach_pot_reichweite
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id 
ORDER BY reach DESC limit 100

SELECT
post_carousels as carousels,
post_images as images,
post_reels as reels,
post_carousels + post_images + post_reels as total   
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id

SELECT
story_images as image,
story_videos as video,
story_images + story_videos as total   
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr
AND profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id

options.content: YouTube | ${Month:text} $Jahr

targets.rawSql:
SELECT videostarts, CASE monat
        WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT(tag," Jan.")
        WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT(tag," Feb.")
        WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT(tag," März")
        WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT(tag," Apr.")
        WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT(tag," Mai")
        WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT(tag," Juni")
        WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT(tag," Juli")
        WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT(tag," Aug.")
        WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT(tag," Sep.")
        WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT(tag," Okt.")
        WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT(tag," Nov.")
        WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT(tag," Dez.")
        END as d_time, DATE(jahr,monat,tag) as time
FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics_per_day
WHERE CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 13 THEN TRUE 
ELSE monat = $month_as_number END
AND jahr = $Jahr
AND profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id
ORDER BY time ASC

SELECT 
time as Datum,
CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(duration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(duration,60) AS String)  END) as Dauer,
  CONCAT(
  CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(DIV(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)  END ,
  ":",CASE WHEN LENGTH(CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String))<2 THEN CONCAT("0",CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)) ELSE CAST(MOD(averageViewDuration,60) AS String)  END) as averageViewTime,
  Round(estimatedMinutesWatched/60,0) as averageViewTime,

  Round(estimatedMinutesWatched/60,0) as sehVolumen,
title,
views, 
link,
likes + dislikes + comments + shares as interactions,
averageViewPercentage,
abo_change,
--FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_top_videos_nach_videostarts_zeitraum_genutzt
FROM `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly${dataset_suffix}.youtubeAnalyticsTopVideos${topvideos_suffix}` as youtube
WHERE profileId =106046
--WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND Profil = "Tagesschau"
ORDER BY views DESC LIMIT 100

SELECT 
Datum,
Dauer,
averageViewTime,
sehVolumen,
title,
views,
link,
likes + dislikes + comments + shares as interactions,
averageViewPercentage,
abo_change,
FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_top_videos_nach_videostarts_zeitraum_veroeffentlicht

WHERE monat = $month_as_number AND jahr = $Jahr AND Profil = "Tagesschau"
ORDER BY views DESC LIMIT 100

options.content:
#### Facebook Interaktionen: 

Ab April 2024: Interaktionen auf Profil-Ebene nicht mehr verfügbar,
stattdessen Post-Daten verwendet.

#### Instagram Interaktionen:
In diesen Daten sind ab Dez 23 Shares für alle Post-Typen enthalten. Vergleiche mit Vormonaten nicht möglich.

# Hinweis:

- Die Langzeittrends beziehen sich zeitlich auf das heutige Datum, nicht auf die Monatsauswahl oben im Dashboard.
- Für die Auswahl 25 Monate werden im Moment nicht die vollen 25 Monate dargestellt, sondern die seit Ausweisung in Minerva (Mai 2023) verfügbaren Daten.

targets.rawSql:
WITH fb as(
SELECT 
 page_follows AS fb_followers,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
ig as(
SELECT 
 followers AS ig_followers,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
yt as(
SELECT 
 abonnements AS yt_followers,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
tt as(
SELECT 
 followers AS tt_followers,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
)
SELECT 	fb_followers,
				ig_followers,
				yt_followers,
				tt_followers,
        fb_followers + ig_followers + yt_followers + tt_followers as total,
				CASE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM fb.datum)
        WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT("Jan. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT("Feb. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT("März ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT("Apr. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT("Mai ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT("Juni ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT("Juli ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT("Aug. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT("Sep. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT("Okt. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT("Nov. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT("Dez. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        END as datum,
        CASE 
        WHEN $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate < 7 THEN "bar"
        ELSE "line" END as typ
FROM fb
JOIN ig ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from ig.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from ig.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
JOIN yt ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from yt.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from yt.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
JOIN tt ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from tt.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from tt.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
ORDER BY fb.datum ASC

WITH fb as(
SELECT 
 views_10s AS Videostarts,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.facebook_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_fb_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
ig as(
SELECT 
 videostarts AS Videostarts,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.instagram_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_insta_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
yt as(
SELECT 
 videostarts_zeitraum_genutzt AS Videostarts,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.youtube_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_yt_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
),
tt as(
SELECT 
 videostarts AS Videostarts,
  DATE(jahr, monat, 1) as datum
FROM Quintly_frozen.tiktok_metrics
WHERE profileId = $tagesschau_tiktok_id
AND monat != 13
AND DATE(jahr,monat,1) BETWEEN DATE_SUB(DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE("$todayDate")),EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE("$todayDate")),1), INTERVAL $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate - 1 MONTH) AND DATE("$langzeittrends_toDate")
)
SELECT 	fb.Videostarts as fb_videostarts,
				ig.Videostarts as ig_videostarts,
				yt.Videostarts as yt_videostarts,
				tt.Videostarts as tt_videostarts,
        fb.Videostarts + ig.Videostarts + yt.Videostarts + tt.Videostarts as total,
				CASE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM fb.datum)
        WHEN 1 THEN CONCAT("Jan. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 2 THEN CONCAT("Feb. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 3 THEN CONCAT("März ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 4 THEN CONCAT("Apr. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 5 THEN CONCAT("Mai ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 6 THEN CONCAT("Juni ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 7 THEN CONCAT("Juli ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 8 THEN CONCAT("Aug. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 9 THEN CONCAT("Sep. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 10 THEN CONCAT("Okt. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 11 THEN CONCAT("Nov. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT("Dez. ", EXTRACT(YEAR FROM fb.datum))
        END as datum,
        CASE 
        WHEN $langzeittrends_anzahl_monate < 7 THEN "bar"
        ELSE "line" END as typ
FROM fb
JOIN ig ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from ig.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from ig.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
JOIN yt ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from yt.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from yt.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
JOIN tt ON (EXTRACT(MONTH from tt.datum) = EXTRACT(MONTH from fb.datum) AND EXTRACT(YEAR from tt.datum) = EXTRACT(YEAR from fb.datum))
ORDER BY fb.datum ASC

query.rawSql:
WITH all_months AS(
  SELECT "Januar" as monat, 1 as monat_num
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Februar", 2
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "März", 3
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "April", 4
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Mai", 5
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Juni", 6
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Juli", 7
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "August", 8
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "September", 9
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Oktober", 10
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "November", 11
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Dezember", 12
  UNION ALL
  SELECT "Jahr", 13
)
SELECT monat FROM all_months
WHERE CASE  
WHEN $Jahr = 2023 THEN monat NOT IN ("Januar","Februar","März","April","Mai")
--WHEN $Jahr = 2024 AND CURRENT_DATE > "2024-09-07" THEN monat NOT IN ("September", "Oktober", "November", "Dezember", "Jahr")
WHEN $Jahr = 2024 AND CURRENT_DATE > "2024-09-07" THEN monat IN ("Januar","Februar","März","April","Mai","Juni", "Juli","August")
WHEN $Jahr = 2024 AND CURRENT_DATE < "2024-09-07" THEN monat IN ("Januar","Februar","März","April","Mai","Juni", "Juli") 
--ELSE monat IN ("Januar","Februar","März","April","Mai","Juni", "Juli", "August", "September", "Oktober", "November", "Dezember") 
END
--ELSE monat NOT IN ("August","September", "Oktober", "November", "Dezember", "Jahr") END

SELECT
CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 1 THEN "Januar"
WHEN 2 THEN "Februar"
WHEN 3 THEN "März"
WHEN 4 THEN "April"
WHEN 5 THEN "Mai"
WHEN 6 THEN "Juni"
WHEN 7 THEN "Juli"
WHEN 8 THEN "August"
WHEN 9 THEN "September"
WHEN 10 THEN "Oktober"
WHEN 11 THEN "November"
WHEN 12 THEN "Dezember"
WHEN 13 THEN ""
END

SELECT
CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 1 THEN "Jan."
WHEN 2 THEN "Feb."
WHEN 3 THEN "März"
WHEN 4 THEN "Apr."
WHEN 5 THEN "Mai"
WHEN 6 THEN "Juni"
WHEN 7 THEN "Juli"
WHEN 8 THEN "Aug."
WHEN 9 THEN "Sep."
WHEN 10 THEN "Okt."
WHEN 11 THEN "Nov."
WHEN 12 THEN CASE "${Monat:text}" WHEN "Jahr" THEN "Jahr" ELSE "Dez." END
END

SELECT
CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 1 THEN "Dez."
WHEN 2 THEN "Jan."
WHEN 3 THEN "Feb."
WHEN 4 THEN "März"
WHEN 5 THEN "Apr."
WHEN 6 THEN "Mai"
WHEN 7 THEN "Juni"
WHEN 8 THEN "Juli"
WHEN 9 THEN "Aug."
WHEN 10 THEN "Sep."
WHEN 11 THEN "Okt."
WHEN 12 THEN "Nov."
WHEN 13 THEN ""
END

SELECT CASE "$Monat"
WHEN "Jahr" THEN CAST($Jahr - 1 AS STRING)
ELSE CAST(EXTRACT(YEAR from DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr,$month_as_number,1),INTERVAL 1 MONTH)) AS STRING) END

SELECT
CASE 
WHEN ($month_as_number = 13 AND DATE($Jahr+1, 1, 7) > CURRENT_DATE()) THEN FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', CURRENT_DATE())
WHEN $month_as_number = 13 THEN CONCAT("07.01.",CAST($Jahr+1 AS STRING))
WHEN DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr,$month_as_number,7), INTERVAL 1 MONTH) > CURRENT_DATE() THEN FORMAT_DATE('%d.%m.%Y', CURRENT_DATE())
ELSE 
CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 12 THEN CONCAT("07.01.",CAST($Jahr+1 AS STRING))
ELSE CONCAT("07.", CAST($month_as_number+1 AS STRING), ".$Jahr") END END

SELECT CASE "${Monat:text}"
WHEN "Jahr" THEN "Veränderung zum Vorjahr"
ELSE "Veränderung zum Vormonat" END

SELECT CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 13 THEN CAST(0 AS STRING)
ELSE CAST(EXTRACT(MONTH FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $month_as_number, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)) AS STRING) END
SELECT CAST(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATE_SUB(DATE($Jahr, $month_as_number, 1), INTERVAL 1 MONTH)) AS STRING)

SELECT CASE $month_as_number
WHEN 13 THEN "monat = $month_from_last_year AND jahr = $last_year"
ELSE "monat = $last_month AND jahr = $year_from_last_month" END

SELECT CAST(number AS STRING) FROM (
SELECT
CASE "$Monat"
WHEN "Januar" THEN 1
WHEN "Februar" THEN 2
WHEN "März" THEN 3
WHEN "April" THEN 4
WHEN "Mai" THEN 5
WHEN "Juni" THEN 6
WHEN "Juli" THEN 7
WHEN "August" THEN 8
WHEN "September" THEN 9
WHEN "Oktober" THEN 10
WHEN "November" THEN 11
WHEN "Dezember" THEN 12
WHEN "Jahr" THEN 13
END as number)

SELECT CASE
WHEN CURRENT_DATE > DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR from CURRENT_DATE), EXTRACT(MONTH from CURRENT_DATE), 7) THEN DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR from DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 MONTH)), EXTRACT(MONTH from DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 1 MONTH)), 1)
ELSE DATE(EXTRACT(YEAR from DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 2 MONTH)), EXTRACT(MONTH from DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE, INTERVAL 2 MONTH)), 1) END

SELECT CASE
WHEN $Monat = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() < DATE($Jahr + 1, 1, 7) THEN "" 
WHEN CURRENT_DATE() > DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr,$Monat,7),INTERVAL 1 MONTH) AND $Jahr <= 2024 THEN "_frozen"
WHEN $Jahr < 2021 THEN ""
WHEN $Monat = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 1, 7) THEN "_frozen"
WHEN CURRENT_DATE() < DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr,$Monat,8),INTERVAL 1 MONTH) THEN ""
WHEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,$Monat,1)) <= DATE(2023,05,31) THEN ""
ELSE "" END

SELECT
CASE
WHEN $Monat = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() < DATE($Jahr + 1, 1, 7) THEN ""
WHEN $Jahr < 2021 THEN ""
WHEN $Monat = 13 AND CURRENT_DATE() > DATE($Jahr, 1, 7) THEN CONCAT("_final_",CAST($Jahr AS STRING))
WHEN CURRENT_DATE() < DATE_ADD(DATE($Jahr,$Monat,8),INTERVAL 1 MONTH) THEN ""
WHEN LAST_DAY(DATE($Jahr,$Monat,1)) <= DATE(2023,11,30) THEN CONCAT("_final_youtube_",CAST($Jahr AS STRING),"_", CAST($Monat AS STRING))
ELSE CONCAT("_final_",CAST($Jahr AS STRING),"_", CAST($Monat AS STRING)) END
